data.description: Looking to escape the hustle and bustle? Come and check out this cottage style country feeling home. Situated on 3.5 fenced acres. Plenty of room to spread out and make it your own. The original home encompasses the kitchen and dining area, family room with a wood burning brick fireplace. 3 bedrooms  2 baths one which is in the master. Split bedroom plan. Utility room.The addition was done in 2006 it is huge 32Lx26w with lots of windows and vaulted ceilings and french doors to the outdoor large pool area. You also have a full bath off of this area. The outside garage is great  22x24 with a large loft for extra storage. New drain field installed in 2023. The whole home was re-shingled in 2006 when the addition was done. Wood siding on home is T111. Garage is hardy board. Solar hot water heater. This home is within 5 minutes of 75 making it an ideal location. Call today too see this peaceful private home! Sellers will review all reasonable offers.
